            "label": "Quick answer",
            "text": "<p>Custom trophies are made by <strong>designing the piece, selecting and shaping the material (cut crystal/acrylic, cast/pressed metal, machined wood), then laser engraving or UV printing names and logos, plating/polishing, and quality-checking</strong> before dispatch — all in-house at Meru Trophy, Bangalore. WhatsApp +91 78922 07252.</p>"
